{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@_NSRange","text":"NSRange","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"range","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"withCoordinates:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"const","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"coords","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"count:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSUInteger","text":"NSUInteger","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"count","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"range","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The range of vertices to replace. The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"location"},{"type":"text","text":" field indicates"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the first vertex you are replacing, with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"type":"text","text":" being the first vertex, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"being the second vertex, and so on. The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"length"},{"type":"text","text":" field indicates the number"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of vertices to replace."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"coords","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of coordinates defining part of the shape. The data in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this array is copied to the shape’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinates"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"count","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The number of coordinates from the ","type":"text"},{"code":"coords","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" array to insert in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"place of the coordinates in ","type":"text"},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". The sum of ","type":"text"},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"’s length and this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"count must not exceed the number of items currently in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"coordinates","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the shape is currently visible on the map as an annotation, it is redrawn"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"immediately. If the shape is part of an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" object, you must"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"explicitly set the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/shape"},{"type":"text","text":" property in order for any style"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"layers that use the source to be redrawn.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is greater than the "},{"code":"length","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" field of "},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", some vertices will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"effectively be inserted into the shape. On the other hand, if "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is less"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"than the "},{"code":"length","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" field of "},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", some vertices will effectively be removed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" extends beyond the shape’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"coordinates","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property, an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSRangeException","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is raised. If you want to append new vertices to the shape,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-appendCoordinates:count:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint\/replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint\/replacecoordinatesinrange:withcoordinates:count:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPoint(im)replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Replaces the vertices at the given range in the shape with the specified number"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of vertices from a given C array."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource/shape":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"shape","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"shape","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource\/shape","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/shape","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The contents of the source. A shape can represent a GeoJSON geometry, a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature, or a collection of features."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPoint/replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint\/replacecoordinatesinrange:withcoordinates:count:","type":"topic","title":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Replaces the vertices at the given range in the shape with the specified number","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of vertices from a given C array.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint\/replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentati